[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1058[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     # Simplified: identify the most critical state features
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1059[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     # (In production, use interpretability methods on the neural network)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1060[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     icu_occ = state[0] if len(state) > 0 else 0
