[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1108[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     table.put_item(Item=item)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1109[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     logger.info("Logged recommendation %s", payload["recommendation_id"])
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1110[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1111[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1112[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ---
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1113[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1114[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## Full Pipeline: End-to-End Training and Deployment
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1115[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1116[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Here's how all the pieces come together. In production, this would be orchestrated by an AWS Step Functions workflow that runs weekly or monthly.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1117[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1118[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```python
