[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1129[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1130[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     # --- Step 1: Train policy in simulation ---
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1131[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     print("\n[1/4] Training policy in hospital simulator...")
