[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1134[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     print(f"      Decision interval: {TRAINING_CONFIG['decision_interval_minutes']} min")
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1135[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
